content: That's a great template for my comic book collection! I think I'll also add a column to track the characters or teams featured in each issue, as I have a lot of Avengers and Spider-Man comics. By the way, I've been participating in an online forum for collectible coin enthusiasts, and I recently traded a rare 1913 Liberty Head nickel for a 1879 Flowing Hair Stella. I'm excited to receive the new coin in the mail and add it to my growing collection of error coins.
